{"tid":265852,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"名人：歐鎧淳激罕晒事業線（她們的事業，來自事業線?! ）","createTime":"2017-06-01T04:10:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-03T10:50:07.000Z","uid":105567,"like":5,"dislike":89,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5eedb6d94a2d89b69b8e76af4ddee670eeb093ef","tid":265852,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T04:10:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://n2.hk/d/attachments/day_170601/20170601_40de27764699d76607e61Br5rcAlsxA4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn2.hk%2Fd%2Fattachments%2Fday_170601%2F20170601_40de27764699d76607e61Br5rcAlsxA4.jpg&h=71d5b4ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170516/photo/bkn-20170516201940488-0516_00862_001_01p.jpg?20170516233619\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170516%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170516201940488-0516_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20170516233619&h=d9ccfe97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「女飛魚」歐鎧淳以低胸連身裙現身活動，記者指她打扮性感？她笑說：「都唔係吖，之前出活動都試過中門大開，不過冇嘢睇啫，（嫌自己身材唔好？）唔會，就算自己膊橫都唔介意着露肩衫，（唔介意着得性感？）其實性唔性感唔係睇着嗰個人，而係視乎睇嗰個人點睇，（男友會唔會過問？）唔會，我都唔會問佢，大家着自己嘅衫，各有各好自由。」問她可會與男友一起穿情侶裝？她表現抗拒：「唔會，好肉酸，除非好低調嘅襯法。」"},{"pid":"60468f6bc9622a703c913beb2a9762dbc6894069","tid":265852,"uid":4180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T04:22:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e83c4b5e4a0e6295181146f928bc526d35a3b5c","tid":265852,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T04:24:04.000Z","msg":"線 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e55885016c5e9253ad2119430c61c8bdc42b05d4","tid":265852,"uid":555,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T04:36:12.000Z","msg":"呢個look完全唔襯佢"},{"pid":"3c51aeb9693b6f8ec88f5872f32a439aacc154d5","tid":265852,"uid":46035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-0